WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 7=

01:53.328 --> 01:54.248
What's the matter?

01:56.407 --> 02:00.608
Ding told me you've accepted the role
as Prefect of Jingzhao Prefecture.

02:01.207 --> 02:04.048
In a few days, you'll take up
your post at Jingzhao Prefecture.

02:04.767 --> 02:05.847
Indeed.

02:06.808 --> 02:07.608
Why?

02:08.807 --> 02:11.807
You've been idle for years,
and you've got the leg problem.

02:12.168 --> 02:13.487
Why are you being assigned now?

02:16.608 --> 02:17.848
Didn't you tell me

02:18.328 --> 02:19.647
not to get trapped

02:20.247 --> 02:22.848
and become a show in others' eyes?

02:23.328 --> 02:26.008
Now I'm pulling myself together,
accepting His Majesty's assignment.

02:26.767 --> 02:29.487
What? Aren't you pleased?

02:38.767 --> 02:40.008
Of course I'm pleased.

03:06.207 --> 03:07.008
Wuyou.

03:36.568 --> 03:37.448
What are you doing?

03:39.128 --> 03:40.207
Just stay silent.

03:41.647 --> 03:43.888
That was Sister-in-law leaving just now?

03:44.807 --> 03:45.728
You go back first.

03:46.927 --> 03:49.687
She's been going out a lot lately.
Who's she meeting?

03:55.008 --> 03:57.647
Wuyou, I have told you

03:57.967 --> 03:59.608
that we are all your family.

04:00.008 --> 04:02.927
If you have any problem
you can't solve, just tell us.

04:26.048 --> 04:26.848
Here.

04:27.768 --> 04:28.687
Here.

04:30.728 --> 04:31.887
This is good wine.

04:47.792 --> 04:49.424
(Mo Xiuwen)

04:51.927 --> 04:53.648
So this is that master's residence?

04:54.367 --> 04:55.168
Yes.

04:56.208 --> 04:57.608
What is your mom doing?

04:59.007 --> 05:01.608
These years, after Father's death,

05:01.648 --> 05:03.024
(Sacred Tablet of Late Husband, Mo Xiuwen)
Mom became superstitious,

05:03.024 --> 05:04.088
always praying to deities.

05:04.408 --> 05:06.807
She desperately wanted
to see Father again.

05:07.247 --> 05:10.408
At first, she just spent money,
nothing serious.

05:11.648 --> 05:14.728
But recently, Ms. Zhou
introduced her Immortal Master Wang.

05:14.728 --> 05:17.007
He claims he has powers
to commune with the dead

05:17.048 --> 05:18.648
and can help people see the dead.

05:19.048 --> 05:22.648
He had Mother drink water
from wells at Zi hour every day.

05:26.528 --> 05:28.807
He asked her to eat
raw and uncooked food.

05:32.127 --> 05:33.968
He also asked her to bathe
in black dog's blood,

05:36.168 --> 05:38.208
and made her copy scriptures
with her own blood.

05:47.968 --> 05:50.208
I hate copying scriptures.

05:50.648 --> 05:53.408
Why these frauds
all use the same tricks?

05:54.168 --> 05:57.528
That fraud promised
if she perseveres for forty-nine days,

05:57.567 --> 05:58.687
she will finally see ghosts.

05:58.687 --> 06:01.007
With this mortal form,
I seek to commune with the dead.

06:01.007 --> 06:03.768
Across the three realms,
life and death are separated.

06:03.927 --> 06:07.007
I implore divine power
to light the way to enlightenment!

06:20.247 --> 06:21.088
Drink it.

06:21.848 --> 06:25.088
B-But how could I possibly
swallow the fire?

06:46.408 --> 06:47.208
Open your eyes.

07:09.728 --> 07:10.608
Xiuwen.

07:12.208 --> 07:13.447
Do you see him?

07:21.608 --> 07:24.608
Mom says Immortal Master Wang
truly has great powers.

07:25.048 --> 07:26.648
But anyone starving for over a month

07:26.648 --> 07:28.088
and inhaling that smoke

07:28.127 --> 07:29.288
could see things.

07:29.807 --> 07:32.007
That Immortal Master Wang
is obviously a fraud.

07:33.247 --> 07:35.807
Have you told your uncle any of this

07:35.968 --> 07:37.528
or tried reasoning with your mom?

07:39.127 --> 07:40.608
Ever since Father's death,

07:40.807 --> 07:42.247
Mom was utterly heartbroken.

07:42.528 --> 07:44.487
She even wanted to go after
Father into the netherworld.

07:44.768 --> 07:47.408
She attempted suicide several times,
but was stopped each time.

07:47.648 --> 07:50.528
It terrified everyone in our mansion.

07:50.687 --> 07:52.007
We feared she'd do it again.

07:52.288 --> 07:54.327
She had attempted suicide before?

07:56.848 --> 08:00.007
But after turning to these dark rituals,

08:00.567 --> 08:02.768
she stopped attempting suicide.

08:03.247 --> 08:05.088
I knew this is all illusory.

08:05.608 --> 08:09.408
But it's a good thing
if it calms Mom and gives her hope.

08:10.648 --> 08:13.127
But I never expected that fraud
to exploit her so vilely,

08:13.408 --> 08:15.528
torturing her with such absurd tricks!

08:17.528 --> 08:18.447
Go report this.

08:18.768 --> 08:20.048
Report? Are you...

08:20.648 --> 08:21.848
But what about Mom?

08:22.367 --> 08:24.048
Grave illnesses need potent cures.

08:24.927 --> 08:27.048
Your mom has had this dream
for eight years.

08:27.247 --> 08:30.007
Now it's destroying her.
It's time for her to wake up.

08:30.352 --> 08:33.104
(Qiongying Residence)

08:52.248 --> 08:53.447
Zhao Desheng?

08:53.927 --> 08:54.727
Yes.

08:55.607 --> 08:56.528
Zhao Desheng,

08:58.368 --> 09:00.008
born in Hongzhou City, Jiangnan region.

09:01.008 --> 09:02.368
He was a hooligan.

09:03.048 --> 09:05.528
Relying on government contacts
left by his father,

09:06.048 --> 09:08.488
he became a hired thug
of Constable Li Zhongliang,

09:09.567 --> 09:11.927
exploiting a fortune
under pretense of authority.

09:12.248 --> 09:14.488
When floods struck outside Hongzhou,

09:14.847 --> 09:17.687
he deliberately delayed rescue
to extort victims,

09:18.048 --> 09:19.967
causing the death
of Provincial Governor's son.

09:20.488 --> 09:23.648
After the incident,
he changed his name and hid all the way,

09:24.488 --> 09:27.248
posing as an immortal master,
swindling for profit.

09:28.008 --> 09:31.727
But he only knew my birth chart,

09:32.927 --> 09:34.847
and then could tell
my husband had passed.

09:36.048 --> 09:39.488
Ms. Zhou told him everything.

09:39.888 --> 09:40.888
Ms. Zhou?

09:42.687 --> 09:45.327
Zhao Desheng bribed Ms. Zhou heavily.

09:46.368 --> 09:48.488
Ms. Zhou sold him all your details.

09:48.567 --> 09:51.687
And then she introduced you to him.

09:53.368 --> 09:54.488
Impossible!

09:55.488 --> 09:58.888
Do you think Ms. Zhou would never
leak your information for money,

09:59.288 --> 10:01.408
or Ms. Zhou would never harm you?

10:01.988 --> 10:05.207
Do you know how famous you are
among those charlatans and scoundrels?

10:05.927 --> 10:09.408
Many of them know you spend lavishly,

10:09.408 --> 10:10.368
and are easily deceived.

10:10.528 --> 10:13.408
They all fight
to buy information from Ms. Zhou.

10:14.207 --> 10:16.648
Fifty guan, a hundred guan.

10:17.248 --> 10:19.447
Some are even willing
to pay two hundred guan.

10:20.288 --> 10:22.447
Zhao Desheng wasn't the highest bidder,

10:22.648 --> 10:25.128
but he is the one willing
to offer the most commissions.

10:25.128 --> 10:27.408
After the fraud,
he took a forty percent cut

10:27.807 --> 10:31.648
from the money you donated,
and Ms. Zhou took sixty.

10:33.967 --> 10:36.727
Now Zhao Desheng awaits trial
in Jingzhao Prefecture.

10:37.567 --> 10:39.207
He probably won't be
released in his life.

10:39.607 --> 10:40.248
But...

10:41.967 --> 10:46.207
Ms. Zhou has been staying in our family
and watching me grow up.

10:48.087 --> 10:49.648
Twenty guan for introducing someone.

10:50.807 --> 10:52.528
Fifty guan for a single talisman.

10:52.927 --> 10:55.488
Two hundred guan
for a single offering ceremony.

10:55.488 --> 10:56.727
Such huge profits!

10:57.128 --> 10:57.967
Money,

10:58.768 --> 10:59.727
power,

11:00.408 --> 11:01.288
and time

11:01.847 --> 11:03.327
could change someone the most.

11:05.687 --> 11:09.927
It could turn someone you once knew well
into the one completely unfamiliar.

11:15.327 --> 11:18.288
I intercepted Ms. Zhou when she
tried to flee to escape justice.

11:18.967 --> 11:20.807
She's locked up
in the woodshed right now.

11:21.488 --> 11:22.807
After all, she's your maid.

11:22.807 --> 11:23.967
I should let you decide

11:25.048 --> 11:26.447
what to do about her.

11:29.567 --> 11:30.447
But I...

11:31.807 --> 11:34.528
But I did dream of Xiuwen.

11:37.008 --> 11:40.087
I did dream of him.

11:58.927 --> 12:00.687
I often dream

12:01.368 --> 12:02.447
of my mother.

12:05.248 --> 12:09.008
I really want to see him one more time.

12:09.488 --> 12:11.648
Even in dreams.

12:15.847 --> 12:18.327
Even in dreams.

12:31.536 --> 12:38.727
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

12:38.727 --> 12:39.687
You stop!

12:41.768 --> 12:43.648
Prince Ding is here to take up his post.

12:44.447 --> 12:45.727
Show me the letter and token.

12:45.727 --> 12:46.528
How dare you!

12:47.128 --> 12:48.688
I'm only following procedures.

12:49.208 --> 12:51.288
Your Highness,
please don't make this difficult.

12:53.807 --> 12:54.447
Show him.

13:00.288 --> 13:01.424
Prince Ding has received

13:01.424 --> 13:04.368
an imperial decree to assume the post
of Prefect of Jingzhao Prefecture.

13:04.687 --> 13:05.567
Want to see it?

13:06.207 --> 13:07.048
I wouldn't dare.

13:08.648 --> 13:09.687
Prince Ding, please.

13:13.888 --> 13:14.687
You, carry me.

13:18.368 --> 13:19.447
I have other duties.

13:20.327 --> 13:23.727
From now on, carrying me
to duty daily is your duty.

13:26.687 --> 13:27.288
Yes.

13:35.408 --> 13:39.231
(Hall of Impartial Justice)

13:42.807 --> 13:44.488
- Greetings, Prefect.
- Greetings, Prefect.

13:47.207 --> 13:49.136
(Deputy Prefect of Jingzhao Prefecture)
I'm Deputy Prefect of Jingzhao Prefecture,

13:49.136 --> 13:50.248
(Zheng Zuoshi)
Zheng Zuoshi.

13:50.807 --> 13:52.168
Greetings, Prefect.

13:55.528 --> 13:57.567
Both of you have been out
for duty since Mou hour,

13:57.847 --> 13:59.008
and only just returned now.

13:59.847 --> 14:00.768
Any findings?

14:01.087 --> 14:01.927
Prefect,

14:03.128 --> 14:06.008
I accompanied Deputy Prefect Zheng
to inspect the East Market.

14:06.128 --> 14:09.327
The merchants are deeply dissatisfied
with the temporary levies.

14:09.327 --> 14:10.672
(Revenue Clerk of Jingzhao Prefecture)
Some even threatened

14:10.672 --> 14:12.648
(Li Yufeng)
to jointly close shops in protest.

14:12.807 --> 14:13.607
How unruly!

14:13.607 --> 14:15.008
I only took on post today.

14:16.008 --> 14:17.768
When did I order any levies?

14:19.528 --> 14:22.607
You're new here, so you don't know.

14:23.087 --> 14:24.607
Did you order the levies?

14:27.967 --> 14:31.768
The remaining funds in the accounts
of Jingzhao Prefecture have run out.

14:31.888 --> 14:35.927
I asked if you ordered the levies.

14:36.567 --> 14:37.327
Exactly.

14:38.528 --> 14:42.128
Then, Deputy Prefect,
please go appease these merchants.

14:42.408 --> 14:44.488
If they close shops in protest,

14:45.168 --> 14:48.607
don't blame me for charging you
with dereliction of duty.

14:50.528 --> 14:51.607
Understood.

14:56.048 --> 14:57.248
Anything else to report?

14:59.807 --> 15:00.888
If not...

15:02.704 --> 15:05.048
(Military Secretary
of Jingzhao Prefecture, Wang Suwu)

15:05.048 --> 15:06.248
You are Prince Ding?

15:06.648 --> 15:08.048
Only official rank matters here.

15:08.648 --> 15:11.128
You should address me as Prefect.

15:13.567 --> 15:17.967
I am Military Secretary Wang Suwu.
Greetings, Prefect.

15:20.927 --> 15:23.847
The murdered soldiers and civilians
of Xiaoshui County at Suixue Pass

15:24.408 --> 15:28.567
and 27 wronged souls of my Wang family,

15:28.888 --> 15:30.447
send you their regards.

15:33.807 --> 15:34.488
How dare you!

15:35.248 --> 15:38.888
I am the Military Secretary,
appointed by the Ministry of Personnel,

15:38.888 --> 15:40.288
ranked Grade Seven, lower class.

15:41.447 --> 15:44.567
May I ask what position do you hold?

15:44.687 --> 15:46.008
Of what rank?

15:46.087 --> 15:48.687
What authority do you have
to reprimand me here?

15:48.927 --> 15:49.528
You!

15:51.888 --> 15:53.567
The regards from murdered soldiers
and civilians of Xiaoshui County

15:54.488 --> 15:55.727
and 27 wronged souls

15:56.927 --> 15:58.927
of your Wang family,

16:00.288 --> 16:01.087
I have

16:02.768 --> 16:03.648
received them.

16:05.807 --> 16:06.307
(Prince Ding's Mansion)
Your Highness.

16:11.607 --> 16:13.888
Ms. Wen is waiting for you
in the main hall.

16:16.607 --> 16:18.008
If not for Li this time,

16:18.727 --> 16:20.368
I'd still be kept in the dark,

16:20.847 --> 16:22.408
and nearly made a terrible mistake.

16:25.368 --> 16:27.128
Ever since your elder brother
passed away,

16:27.687 --> 16:30.408
I've been drowning in grief
and couldn't pull myself out,

16:31.687 --> 16:35.927
so I neglected those around me
and showed no concern for Wuyou.

16:37.008 --> 16:40.207
I-I deserve death!

16:40.368 --> 16:41.727
Please don't say that.

16:43.207 --> 16:44.488
You should blame me.

16:45.607 --> 16:49.368
With elder brother gone, I should
have taken better care of you and Wuyou.

16:50.528 --> 16:54.008
It was my oversight
that put you in danger

16:54.567 --> 16:57.048
and allowed Wuyou to be bullied.

16:58.727 --> 17:00.168
How could I blame you?

17:01.327 --> 17:04.127
You haven't had it easy all these years.

17:06.008 --> 17:07.728
I'm glad to see you
pull yourself together.

17:13.807 --> 17:14.607
Xiuyao.

17:16.567 --> 17:17.768
You must pull yourself together.

17:19.407 --> 17:22.288
No matter what,
we should all stick together

17:22.288 --> 17:25.448
and stay safe, which matters the most.

17:26.968 --> 17:28.167
Now that we have Li,

17:29.087 --> 17:31.167
our life will surely get better.

17:40.288 --> 17:42.367
Please thank Li for me.

17:43.448 --> 17:44.647
I shall take my leave.

17:54.688 --> 17:55.968
Where is the Princess Consort?

17:56.968 --> 17:57.768
Her...

18:00.087 --> 18:00.968
Where is Her Highness?

18:13.288 --> 18:13.788
Hurry!

18:16.688 --> 18:17.448
Hurry! Stand still!

18:20.208 --> 18:21.087
Apologize now!

18:23.968 --> 18:27.048
- We have behaved improperly.
- We have behaved improperly

18:27.288 --> 18:28.887
- We bullied our classmate.
- We bullied our classmate.

18:28.887 --> 18:31.208
- We beg you for forgiveness, Young Lord.
- We beg you for forgiveness, Young Lord.

18:42.192 --> 18:45.719
(Qinglu Academy)

18:52.008 --> 18:52.807
What's wrong?

18:53.928 --> 18:56.928
I'm telling you,
I saw it clearly just now.

18:57.208 --> 18:59.847
The parents of those kids
were gritting their teeth in fury.

19:00.208 --> 19:01.567
They're bound to get a beating.

19:02.208 --> 19:04.528
They weren't sincere in their apology.

19:05.768 --> 19:08.208
They apologized
only because they had to.

19:09.048 --> 19:11.288
I was injured
and of higher status than them.

19:11.728 --> 19:14.048
They apologized to me
only because they were scared.

19:14.928 --> 19:15.847
So what?

19:16.928 --> 19:18.407
Who cares if they are sincere?

19:18.847 --> 19:21.008
Today, you need to show them

19:21.248 --> 19:24.448
that even if they are reluctant,
you still can make them apologize.

19:25.008 --> 19:28.208
If they really regret it,
you accept their apology.

19:28.448 --> 19:31.928
If they don't, you can make them fear.

19:32.567 --> 19:33.167
I see.

19:34.448 --> 19:38.968
Besides, today was just
a minor punishment and a stern warning.

19:39.048 --> 19:40.167
If they dare try again,

19:40.367 --> 19:42.327
I will have plenty of ways
to deal with them.

19:42.607 --> 19:43.607
Like what?

19:44.647 --> 19:47.008
Many ways! We have your uncle.

19:47.367 --> 19:49.367
He is now the Prefect
of Jingzhao Prefecture.

19:49.607 --> 19:52.968
Many spoiled brats have been locked up
in Jingzhao Prefecture prison.

19:54.288 --> 19:56.407
Wouldn't that make us bullies
who abuse our power?

19:56.567 --> 19:57.567
Of course not.

19:58.488 --> 20:00.367
If someone commits a crime,
like assault,

20:00.567 --> 20:03.607
shouldn't the Jingzhao Prefecture
protect its citizens?

20:04.087 --> 20:05.327
We are citizens as well.

20:05.847 --> 20:08.567
Moreover,
even if he weren't the Prefect,

20:08.688 --> 20:10.008
he is still your uncle,

20:10.008 --> 20:11.248
and I am his Princess Consort.

20:11.768 --> 20:15.008
He ought to stand up for us
whenever we face trouble.

20:18.728 --> 20:19.647
Uncle.

20:35.567 --> 20:36.567
Where have you been?

20:37.327 --> 20:38.248
Collecting debts.

20:39.847 --> 20:41.327
Aunt took me to the academy

20:41.327 --> 20:43.847
and made those classmates
who bullied me apologize to me.

20:51.448 --> 20:54.528
If the academy is stifling,
you can go to the Chongwen Institute.

20:54.607 --> 20:57.407
I have arranged it.
You can start next month.

20:57.887 --> 20:59.887
I won't leave. I'm not afraid of them.

21:00.647 --> 21:02.208
Right, don't be afraid.

21:04.288 --> 21:06.248
Then I'll let two guards accompany you.

21:07.048 --> 21:08.688
No, thanks, Uncle.

21:08.887 --> 21:10.688
Aunt said she'd have Ding accompany me.

21:11.768 --> 21:13.807
What about a page boy
skilled in martial arts?

21:15.327 --> 21:18.087
For a bunch of kids brawling,
no need for martial arts masters.

21:18.248 --> 21:19.448
Ding alone is enough.

21:22.647 --> 21:23.607
Let's eat.

21:29.887 --> 21:32.008
What's the matter?
Did you burn yourself?

21:34.067 --> 21:34.567
It's okay.

21:34.567 --> 21:37.327
Y-Your Highness,
he has been very busy lately,

21:37.327 --> 21:39.968
with internal heat rising
and causing mouth sores.

21:47.528 --> 21:51.008
During my time on the mountain,
in winter, we couldn't get fresh greens,

21:51.248 --> 21:52.647
and often got mouth sores.

21:52.847 --> 21:54.208
So, I always carry medicine.

21:54.807 --> 21:56.048
Let me apply this for you.

21:56.528 --> 21:58.327
No need, you two eat first.

22:17.768 --> 22:18.567
Open your mouth.

22:24.728 --> 22:25.448
Here?

22:27.807 --> 22:28.607
Here?

22:30.968 --> 22:31.647
Found it.

22:37.968 --> 22:40.327
This medicine is made by me,

22:40.728 --> 22:42.008
so it's not bitter at all.

22:43.248 --> 22:46.448
Your Highness, you've been
shutting yourself in your room all day,

22:46.528 --> 22:47.768
even avoiding the sun.

22:48.288 --> 22:49.488
And you don't like eating.

22:49.807 --> 22:52.288
You're practically inviting these sores.

22:57.167 --> 22:57.688
Done.

23:01.607 --> 23:03.008
Apply it once more tonight.

23:05.048 --> 23:05.768
I'll do it myself.

23:07.248 --> 23:07.748
Okay.

23:12.807 --> 23:15.048
Earlier in the mansion,
I ran into Sister-in-law.

23:18.048 --> 23:19.407
She asked me to thank you for her.

23:22.968 --> 23:23.768
What about you?

23:26.288 --> 23:27.768
You thanked me for Sister-in-law.

23:28.087 --> 23:29.567
Don't you want to thank me yourself?

23:31.768 --> 23:32.288
Thank...

23:32.288 --> 23:34.607
Forget it. We are a couple.

23:35.327 --> 23:37.167
Your sister-in-law is mine.

23:37.528 --> 23:38.847
Your nephew is also mine.

23:39.087 --> 23:40.048
So, no need to thank me.

23:44.807 --> 23:46.807
Have this.
It's to relieve internal heat.

23:48.488 --> 23:49.248
You have some too.

23:52.928 --> 23:53.688
You have some too.

24:03.167 --> 24:04.208
Mo Xiuyao,

24:05.208 --> 24:06.728
let me heal your legs.

24:07.567 --> 24:11.008
Master Helai on Lishan Mountain
is a renowned master physician.

24:11.167 --> 24:14.008
He once wrote the Treatise
on Injuries and Diseases. Heard of it?

24:15.288 --> 24:17.928
I learned how to treat
bone injury from him.

24:18.847 --> 24:21.167
And I treated similar cases
up in the mountains.

24:22.248 --> 24:25.288
Jin has been supporting you
to stand and sit every day.

24:25.567 --> 24:28.647
Your legs can bear some weight,
and aren't completely numb.

24:29.847 --> 24:32.567
Let me try.
There might still be a chance.

24:37.008 --> 24:38.688
Uncle, Aunt, I'm full.

24:38.768 --> 24:41.127
You two enjoy your meal.
I'll go buy some desserts.

24:43.208 --> 24:46.048
Your Highness, Wuyou isn't safe alone.
I'll go protect him. Come on.

24:48.188 --> 24:49.048
- Your Highness.
- Go ahead.

24:49.048 --> 24:49.548
Then I...

24:54.208 --> 24:55.167
Why do you leave?

24:55.167 --> 24:56.327
His Highness is about to get angry.

25:01.768 --> 25:02.448
It's to relieve internal heat.

25:04.567 --> 25:07.327
You know Wei Zhuang,
the steward at my shop, right?

25:07.528 --> 25:09.288
He was my senior at Lishan Academy.

25:10.367 --> 25:12.928
His leg was injured before,
and he has limped for many years.

25:12.928 --> 25:14.607
I'm currently treating him.

25:14.887 --> 25:17.688
He says my treatment works
better than that of the physicians.

25:17.807 --> 25:19.488
And the pain has lessened significantly.

25:20.407 --> 25:23.528
I remember your legs hurt
on cloudy days too, don't they?

25:31.607 --> 25:32.728
Let's eat first.

25:33.567 --> 25:35.448
We'll talk about that later.

25:36.968 --> 25:37.647
Alright.

25:44.400 --> 25:49.136
(Tuisi Pavilion)

25:50.928 --> 25:52.928
My Lady, don't rush.

25:54.208 --> 25:54.887
I don't.

25:57.728 --> 26:00.087
This jade piece is perfect
for the Master's birthday.

26:00.367 --> 26:01.367
Madam will be pleased.

26:03.488 --> 26:04.488
Is this price acceptable?

26:05.288 --> 26:06.488
This item is truly excellent.

26:06.768 --> 26:07.968
Both of you have good taste.

26:07.968 --> 26:09.087
This is quite beautiful.

26:09.928 --> 26:11.887
You two, what else
would you like to see?

26:12.008 --> 26:13.847
The brushwork is elegant,
and the vibe is ethereal.

26:14.008 --> 26:14.968
Truly a fine piece.

26:15.327 --> 26:17.712
Last year in Suzhou, I heard
genuine pieces are hard to find.

26:17.847 --> 26:19.607
Its glaze resembles blood.

26:19.607 --> 26:22.448
Look at this iron sword. The characters
incised at the scabbard throat.

26:22.448 --> 26:23.688
Come on, take a look.

26:24.048 --> 26:28.008
The signature seal stamp is still
clearly identifiable after a century.

26:28.087 --> 26:30.576
This painting was sought out
for me by my friends

26:30.864 --> 26:34.248
in the Grain Tribute Gang
from an old estate in Jiangnan.

26:34.968 --> 26:38.688
If you hang it in your hall,
it will enhance elegance,

26:39.647 --> 26:42.248
and you will also earn a fortune
by reselling it.

26:44.208 --> 26:46.488
Zhou, put the treasure away for now.

26:46.488 --> 26:47.127
Okay.

26:47.647 --> 26:51.488
Don't! I'll take it.

26:52.248 --> 26:54.048
Thank you, dear guests!

26:54.367 --> 26:55.407
This way, please.

26:58.248 --> 27:00.327
Your Highness,
we made a huge profit again.

27:02.448 --> 27:05.048
Back in his days at Lishan Academy,
Senior Wei Zhuang

27:05.208 --> 27:06.488
was already renowned

27:06.488 --> 27:07.688
for his great memory,

27:07.768 --> 27:09.847
and mastery of arithmetic and commerce.

27:10.367 --> 27:13.528
If he had served as an official,
it'd be easy for him to rise and soar.

27:14.087 --> 27:15.367
Running a few shops

27:15.448 --> 27:19.087
is mere child's play for him.

27:20.928 --> 27:22.688
Master Wei is truly formidable.

27:23.647 --> 27:24.647
Murder!

27:27.488 --> 27:28.208
Uncle Wenshen?

27:28.208 --> 27:30.087
Pretend you don't see me.

27:31.968 --> 27:34.008
Ye Wenshen, you villain!

27:35.488 --> 27:37.528
Ye Wenshen, come out now!

27:38.167 --> 27:40.528
Where are you hiding? Come out!

27:40.647 --> 27:41.647
Have you seen him?

27:42.208 --> 27:42.928
No.

27:43.248 --> 27:46.208
If I find you, I'll flay you alive!

27:46.288 --> 27:47.048
Ye Wenshen!

27:48.407 --> 27:49.528
Come out now!

27:50.087 --> 27:51.688
I saw someone heading that way.

27:52.807 --> 27:53.607
Which way?

27:53.728 --> 27:54.528
That way.

27:54.887 --> 27:55.528
Thanks.

28:03.920 --> 28:08.464
(Shende Shop)

28:15.327 --> 28:16.528
What happened exactly?

28:20.968 --> 28:22.288
It's just a misunderstanding.

28:22.887 --> 28:26.048
Mrs. Wang,
the wife of that big and dumb guy,

28:26.887 --> 28:28.407
she often comes to my shop...

28:29.248 --> 28:30.847
She burns incense
and prays for blessings there.

28:31.528 --> 28:33.928
She is devout and generous with money.

28:34.048 --> 28:35.607
You know me.

28:35.807 --> 28:39.968
I interact with everyone
with nothing but gratitude.

28:39.968 --> 28:43.688
So I show her a little extra warmth.

28:44.087 --> 28:45.647
Then rumors started spreading,

28:45.928 --> 28:50.208
saying there's an affair
between her and me.

28:52.288 --> 28:53.847
And that fool believed it

28:54.208 --> 28:55.407
and demanded an explanation.

28:55.528 --> 28:57.407
I thought it's fine.

28:57.407 --> 28:58.887
But before I could utter a word,

28:59.048 --> 29:01.087
he drew a knife and swung it at me.

29:01.488 --> 29:03.728
Thankfully, I was quite agile.

29:03.807 --> 29:06.008
Otherwise, my head
wouldn't be on my shoulders.

29:06.248 --> 29:08.008
I would be chopped to pieces in public!

29:08.367 --> 29:09.288
So is it true?

29:09.288 --> 29:09.928
What?

29:10.208 --> 29:11.647
No way.

29:11.807 --> 29:13.407
Mrs. Wang looks... Let me tell you.

29:13.407 --> 29:14.887
You haven't seen her. She looks...

29:15.367 --> 29:17.647
Even if she's willing, I wouldn't!

29:19.607 --> 29:21.248
I can't go back to Longevity Shop.

29:22.167 --> 29:23.728
My place is also being watched.

29:23.807 --> 29:29.048
Li, let me take shelter at your mansion,

29:29.567 --> 29:30.448
just for a few days.

29:31.048 --> 29:32.488
Why take shelter at my mansion?

29:32.768 --> 29:33.887
Your mansion is safe.

29:33.887 --> 29:35.327
It's Prince Ding's Mansion.

29:35.488 --> 29:39.087
Your husband is Prince Ding,
also the Prefect of Jingzhao Prefecture.

29:39.367 --> 29:41.327
That fool wouldn't dare
cause trouble there!

29:42.607 --> 29:45.968
You've decided. How could I refuse?

29:47.248 --> 29:51.488
Well, Li, you care the most about me.

29:54.847 --> 29:56.887
Your Highness,
I'll get the carriage first.

30:00.728 --> 30:03.847
Li, on second thought,

30:04.087 --> 30:06.248
I need to go back
to Longevity Shop to get some stuff.

30:06.968 --> 30:09.087
I have to stay at your mansion
for a few days.

30:09.208 --> 30:10.448
You go back first.

30:10.728 --> 30:13.048
You aren't afraid
to run into that man again?

30:14.448 --> 30:15.807
I'll go back in via the back door.

30:17.248 --> 30:20.768
Alright, I'll have
a room prepared first.

30:21.528 --> 30:22.407
Good girl.

30:22.448 --> 30:23.208
Your Highness.

30:31.367 --> 30:32.127
Ye Li.

30:34.048 --> 30:35.728
This must be your husband.

30:36.807 --> 30:39.928
Truly, royalty adorned in purple,

30:40.208 --> 30:42.087
and jade belt fitting for a celestial.

30:43.008 --> 30:46.127
This is my uncle, Ye Wenshen,
Master of Longevity Shop.

30:48.087 --> 30:48.887
Niece-in-law.

30:49.768 --> 30:53.248
I might be staying
at your mansion for a while.

30:53.407 --> 30:55.768
I was in a rush today
and forgot to bring a proper gift.

30:55.928 --> 30:58.928
I have high-grade Mengding Shihua tea.

30:59.048 --> 31:00.847
Wait for me. I'll bring some.

31:00.847 --> 31:01.887
The back door is this way?

31:02.768 --> 31:03.567
Wait for me.

31:06.728 --> 31:08.048
He said to stay at our mansion?

31:09.208 --> 31:10.008
Yes.

31:10.567 --> 31:12.607
He got into some trouble.

31:12.847 --> 31:16.048
Someone is demanding his life
outside Longevity Shop.

31:16.048 --> 31:17.208
He's too scared to return,

31:17.847 --> 31:19.807
and he wants to take shelter
at our mansion.

31:21.728 --> 31:23.768
Why doesn't he go back to Ye Mansion?

31:24.327 --> 31:27.208
The most influential
in Ye Mansion is my eldest uncle.

31:27.728 --> 31:29.728
But compared to you,
Prefect of Jingzhao Prefecture,

31:29.728 --> 31:31.728
he's just insignificant.

31:32.087 --> 31:35.048
Uncle Wenshen is clever, seeking refuge
with someone the most powerful.

31:40.647 --> 31:42.448
Are you fine with it?

31:44.327 --> 31:45.407
He is your uncle.

31:45.567 --> 31:47.728
Since you've invited him,
I can only be fine with it.

31:50.928 --> 31:52.647
Have you done all your work today?

31:53.728 --> 31:55.607
Come on. Get in. Let's return together.

31:57.728 --> 31:59.208
- Good!
- Good!

31:59.208 --> 32:00.248
Thank you!

32:01.127 --> 32:02.288
Thank you!

32:02.607 --> 32:03.728
Thank you!

32:04.647 --> 32:05.928
The monkey got loose!

32:18.327 --> 32:19.127
What happened?

32:19.508 --> 32:20.008
Li!

32:20.008 --> 32:22.008
Ye Li! Are you alright?

32:22.008 --> 32:22.928
What happened?

32:32.327 --> 32:34.167
I'm terribly sorry to startle you.

32:34.167 --> 32:36.208
What's wrong with you?
Control your monkey.

32:39.688 --> 32:40.807
It's fine.

32:42.488 --> 32:44.528
Jin, go back now.

32:44.688 --> 32:46.928
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

33:31.567 --> 33:33.607
Qingshuang, what's wrong?

33:35.407 --> 33:37.768
My Lady, a monkey!

33:38.528 --> 33:40.768
A monkey? Impossible.

33:41.248 --> 33:43.488
That monkey has been caught
by the monkey trainer.

33:43.768 --> 33:46.647
But I saw it, truly!

33:46.688 --> 33:49.887
It was in the courtyard, right there.

33:51.407 --> 33:52.847
It even bit me.

33:56.647 --> 33:59.167
Don't be afraid. I'm here.

34:03.167 --> 34:04.248
Monkey!

34:12.287 --> 34:13.048
I don't see it.

34:13.767 --> 34:14.567
Qingshuang.

34:17.687 --> 34:18.448
Qingshuang?

34:26.607 --> 34:27.408
Qingshuang?

34:29.368 --> 34:30.167
Qingshuang.

34:34.287 --> 34:35.328
Where are you, Qingshuang?

34:36.767 --> 34:37.567
Qingshuang.

34:38.968 --> 34:39.767
Qingshuang.

34:41.888 --> 34:42.687
Qingshuang.

35:38.488 --> 35:39.368
Who's there?

35:45.647 --> 35:48.328
Your Highness,
what are you doing here alone?

35:59.368 --> 36:00.167
Monkey.

36:05.528 --> 36:06.808
Where did the monkey go?

36:10.048 --> 36:10.848
Monkey.

36:22.687 --> 36:23.687
What happened?

36:25.087 --> 36:26.048
Monkeys!

36:27.247 --> 36:30.287
So many monkeys!

36:37.968 --> 36:38.767
Found none.

36:43.287 --> 36:44.087
Your Highness.

36:46.687 --> 36:48.048
Are you hurt anywhere?

36:49.008 --> 36:51.408
Sister-in-law, I'm fine. Don't worry.

36:53.488 --> 36:56.488
Xiuyao said you saw monkeys
in the mansion?

37:00.127 --> 37:01.928
You must have been seeing things.

37:02.408 --> 37:03.968
The capital is heavily guarded,

37:04.008 --> 37:05.408
and the mansion has high walls.

37:05.888 --> 37:07.448
Monkeys wouldn't run rampant here.

37:08.008 --> 37:11.687
Jackdaws often perch on the rockery
in the west corner of the backyard.

37:11.687 --> 37:14.328
Not jackdaws. Monkeys!

37:15.647 --> 37:17.607
I did not see wrong.
There really are monkeys!

37:26.167 --> 37:27.448
I know you don't believe me.

37:28.287 --> 37:29.087
But I...

37:35.647 --> 37:36.448
Never mind.

37:37.928 --> 37:38.727
Forget it.

37:44.167 --> 37:46.687
Pass down the order. Stay high alert.

37:47.968 --> 37:50.607
Take men and thoroughly search
the perimeter of the mansion again.

37:51.448 --> 37:52.048
Yes!

37:56.247 --> 38:00.087
Then Wuyou and I will
return to our room first.

38:01.247 --> 38:02.607
Rest well.

38:09.848 --> 38:12.048
Aunt, I take my leave.

38:15.167 --> 38:17.328
Your Highness, are you alright?

38:20.368 --> 38:22.008
Should I call a physician
to examine you?

38:22.008 --> 38:23.328
Let her rest first.

38:24.488 --> 38:25.287
Yes.

38:43.207 --> 38:44.408
I remember you once said

38:45.647 --> 38:47.127
there were monkeys on Lishan Mountain.

38:48.167 --> 38:49.848
Would they sneak into the academy?

38:54.287 --> 38:55.087
Yes.

38:58.087 --> 38:59.607
They always came in to steal things.

39:00.928 --> 39:02.607
Not only did they
steal the meals I made,

39:03.848 --> 39:05.008
but also stole my books.

39:05.808 --> 39:07.528
There were so many people
in Lishan Academy.

39:07.767 --> 39:10.607
Weren't monkeys afraid of people?
They even stole things?

39:10.968 --> 39:13.647
Those monkeys were very bold.

39:15.408 --> 39:16.808
I got bitten by them.

39:18.808 --> 39:19.687
See?

39:32.408 --> 39:33.207
It's fine.

39:34.368 --> 39:37.247
I already had Jin patrol the backyard.

39:39.287 --> 39:40.607
Get some rest now.

39:42.127 --> 39:44.488
I promise you won't be scared
by any more monkeys.

40:07.368 --> 40:08.167
I can't sleep.

40:12.247 --> 40:13.167
I'll stay with you.

40:15.247 --> 40:16.488
I won't leave before you fall asleep.

41:05.048 --> 41:09.448
Your Highness, the mansion has been
searched. No monkeys were seen.

41:10.647 --> 41:12.287
Perhaps the Princess Consort
was mistaken?

41:13.767 --> 41:15.808
Send more men
to patrol throughout the night.

41:17.767 --> 41:18.567
Yes.

41:26.640 --> 41:28.880
(Tuisi Pavilion)

41:34.408 --> 41:36.048
An invitation from Prince Li's Mansion?

41:36.048 --> 41:37.328
Is it from Princess Li?

41:37.528 --> 41:40.287
She's inviting you to go on
a painted boat cruise on Chengxin Lake?

41:43.368 --> 41:44.167
I won't go.

41:46.008 --> 41:48.928
(Invitation from Dong Mu of Prince Li's Mansion)
Have you been troubled by the nightmare?

41:50.087 --> 41:51.528
I said it wasn't a nightmare!

41:53.767 --> 41:57.048
I saw many monkeys in the mansion.

41:58.928 --> 42:01.607
Alright. Regardless of
whether it's real or fake,

42:01.607 --> 42:02.968
His Highness believes it.

42:05.048 --> 42:05.968
Why do you say that?

42:07.888 --> 42:09.287
I heard it from Jin.

42:09.368 --> 42:12.048
Today, as soon as His Highness
arrived at the Prefecture, he ordered

42:12.048 --> 42:13.727
that no more monkey shows in the city.

42:13.727 --> 42:16.448
He's doing it because he fears
you might get scared by monkeys again.

42:18.008 --> 42:18.808
Order?

42:19.808 --> 42:22.488
Does Jingzhao Prefecture
have the authority to do so?

42:23.087 --> 42:24.848
He asked the monkey trainers to leave?

42:26.368 --> 42:30.687
It said to be an order, but His Highness
compensated them out of his own pocket.

42:30.767 --> 42:33.368
The men from Jingzhao Prefecture
sent the compensation one by one.

42:33.368 --> 42:35.727
Those monkey trainers were happy
to leave with compensation.

42:40.240 --> 42:42.512
(Preview)

42:43.247 --> 42:45.008
Do you think it doesn't look good?

42:45.207 --> 42:47.528
No. Do you feel coolness?

42:48.528 --> 42:51.528
This must be Prince Ding's
newly-wed princess consort.

42:52.127 --> 42:53.968
Headmaster Xu has authored
countless books.

42:54.448 --> 42:57.567
Why are his words not matched by deeds?

42:58.048 --> 43:00.647
As long as I'm with you,
anywhere is good.

43:01.408 --> 43:04.488
Don't you find yourself ridiculous
when you say these things?

43:06.224 --> 43:06.960
(Memorial tablet of Xu Wanzhou)

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
